{"tid":1814084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有冇人記得侵侵話「如果當時教師手上有槍 就唔洗死咁多人」","createTime":"2020-01-06T17:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T18:23:00.000Z","uid":147785,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"01dd7ef4b81436f9ae4108e98de7385c81f42518","tid":1814084,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-43155904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-43155904&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=4bd33641\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-43155904&h=38958c1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-43155904</a><br />\n美國校園槍擊案 死17人 Trump居然話「如果當時教師手上有槍 就唔洗死咁多人」<br />\n<br />\n果陣仲個個話侵侵正一痴線佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算當時教師有槍 只要一日唔管制 槍匪沖入黎亂射 點都死一兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔通侵覺得<strong>死一兩個就無乜大不了?</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但依家睇番先明 侵根本唔係咁既意思<br />\n<br />\n侵係覺得 人民合法持槍 係 民主基礎 立國宗旨<br />\n<br />\n香港依家有板你睇 <span style=\"color: red;\">人民無武力=無民主</span><br />\n<br />\n只有對等武力 政府先會尊重人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以人民持槍權 係原則底線 必須寸步不讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以侵既結論就係 <ins><strong>槍匪點都會出現</strong></ins> 可以做既只有:<br />\n1. 減少槍匪出現頻率(加強監管買槍者精神狀況)<br />\n2. 減少每次槍擊案傷亡數字(全民持槍 儘量即時制止槍匪)<br />\n<br />\n所以先會講左句令人覺得佢係咪痴線既「如果當時教師手上有槍 就唔洗死咁多人」<br />\n<br />\n因為侵背後既意思係: 民主&gt;All, 你想 「槍擊案 間唔中發生 每次傷亡幾個」 定 「終有一日 發生類似香港咁 撕裂整個國家既動亂?」"},{"pid":"78122dffca1e590f5abe27651d375d119b5667b8","tid":1814084,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:59:43.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"d4167d365cdf8b5f75a8fdf7fc3f0b8a027e43d4","tid":1814084,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:00:02.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"3b254dfaba16111523cdd0fd69313071e404ae37","tid":1814084,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:00:35.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"00773b3d3747b85f00374eb1967dfba018c2a9e2","tid":1814084,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:01:00.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"733566329b4405a03d7dd864dc9390683225a10e","tid":1814084,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:01:17.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"efe8a30cb5ab90e687fa6692b9d4df986d9bb4ab","tid":1814084,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:04:39.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"fb0989039b6a0a6b076ed4284e5ff579492fbe64","tid":1814084,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:05:12.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"04b8f45439d1c6b6c95769488767eaa0a98ebda2","tid":1814084,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"b17138b243d55e99ddb35bfc1aba2131ad6730a8","tid":1814084,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:07:16.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"cdcf57805229f5c1591108e3c74db8fc70111aea","tid":1814084,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:10:02.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"39bf290975e70b3873db67a668ce8bf36ad5b9fe","tid":1814084,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:14:55.000Z","msg":"你係香港講槍權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就先真係批比你 <br />\n唔理黃定藍都唔撚制喇"},{"pid":"d8012a4bab087adab1df33fc8246badb6ae50358","tid":1814084,"uid":147785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"39bf290975e70b3873db67a668ce8bf36ad5b9fe","tid":1814084,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20